(---) Tj
T* (name: linux-workstation-setup) Tj
T* (description: Automates the post-installation environment provisioning of a fresh Linux distro) Tj
T* (by updating core packages, applying cohesive custom desktop themes \(like pixel art) Tj
T* (layouts\), configuring dotfiles/shell aliases, and securely installing privacy and development) Tj
T* (suites. Trigger phrases include "Help me spin up my personalized Linux development) Tj
T* (environment," "Run the automation script to configure my custom desktop theme and) Tj
T* (privacy tools," or "Set up a fresh Linux workstation from scratch using my dotfiles.") Tj
T* (---) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (# Instructions) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Receive User Inputs: Ask the user to provide the target Linux distribution \(e.g., Ubuntu,) Tj
T* (Arch\), the path or GitHub repository where their configuration dotfiles are stored, and the) Tj
T* (URL/local path for their custom 4K theme elements \(such as pixel art backgrounds\).) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. System Update & Core Provisioning: Execute package manager updates and install) Tj
T* (essential baseline development packages, a window manager, terminal emulators, and the) Tj
T* (specified privacy applications.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. Configuration Deployment: Clone the dotfiles repository and symlink the configuration) Tj
T* (files to their respective target directories \(e.g., ~/.config/\).) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (4. Theme Application: Move the custom 4K desktop wallpapers into the system) Tj
T* (background directory and modify the window manager or desktop environment theme) Tj
T* (variables to match the intended visual profile.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (5. Quality Check & Verification: Verify successful deployment by checking that the) Tj
T* (configurations load without errors, running a script to test tool availability, and outputting a) Tj
T* (summary table confirming the status of installed tools and active themes.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (6. Final Output: A fully customized, ready-to-use desktop environment matching the user's) Tj
T* (exact development and visual preferences.) Tj
ET
endstream
